.SH OPTIONS
You can optionally tell cyrus-makedirs the Cyrus imapd.conf config file
to use.  /etc/imapd.conf is assumed, if no parameters are given.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR imapd.conf(5),
.BR /etc/default/cyrus-imapd
